          <div class="text-left mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-300 to-indigo-500 mb-6">
              Mediterranean & Coastal Garden Ideas - AI Landscape Visualizer
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-4xl">
              Visualize your own Italian retreat with these user-generated Mediterranean garden designs. Our community uses Hadaa's <strong class="text-white">garden visualizer</strong> to combine sun-drenched pavers with <strong class="text-white">climate-specific plants</strong> like olive trees and lavender. These trusted examples bridge the gap between inspiration and reality, offering a clear vision for your own <strong class="text-white">DIY yard layout</strong> and renovation.
